title: Playoff Picture & Flau'Jae Johnson Interview | WHAT’S BURNIN | SHOWTIME Basketball
itunes:title: Playoff Picture & Flau'Jae Johnson Interview | WHAT’S BURNIN | SHOWTIME Basketball
description:
Jelani McCoy and Josiah Johnson host a special WHAT'S BURNIN episode. The guys breakdown the current NBA playoff picture with a week and half left in the regular season. Plus, they interview the multi-talented high school women's basketball sensation and rapper under Jay-Z's label Flau'Jae Johnson.
